Package: malaviR
Type: Package
Title: An R interface to MalAvi
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vincenzo A", "Ellis", email = "vincenzoaellis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Staffan", "Bensch", email = "staffan.bensch@biol.lu.se", role = "aut"),
    person("Bjorn", "Canback", email = "bjorn.canback@biol.lu.se", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Vincenzo A. Ellis <vincenzoaellis@gmail.com>
Description: Functions for working with data from the MalAvi database of avian
    haemosporidian parasites. The MalAvi website is no longer available online,
    so the database tables and sequence alignment are bundled with the package
    as dated release snapshots. Tools are provided to read those tables and
    alignments, run a local BLAST-like search of a sequence against MalAvi,
    clean repeated haplotypes from an alignment, and relate host taxonomy to a
    modern avian taxonomy.
